    <h1>Multi-orders</h1><div id="preamble">
<div class="sectionbody">
<div class="paragraph">
<p>Go to <strong>System » Orders » Order types » Multi-order</strong> to configure the basic settings for <strong><a href="/en/order-processing/orders/multi-orders">multi-orders</a></strong>. The settings in this menu are the basic settings for all multi-orders. For example, you can specify which order types and order statuses should be available for multi-orders.</p>
</div>
<div class="paragraph instruction">
<p>Configuring multi-orders:</p>
</div>
<div class="olist arabic">
<ol class="arabic">
<li>
<p>Go to <strong>System » Orders » Order types » Multi-order</strong>.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Pay attention to the explanations given in table 1 and carry out the settings as desired.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p><strong>Save</strong> the settings.</p>
</li>
</ol>
</div>
