<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock">Select which order types should be available for multi-orders (multiple selection possible). It is only possible to use the order types listed here for multi-orders.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock"><strong>Item text</strong></p></td>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock">Select which options you want to use for the <strong>item text</strong> column of the stock units that belong to a multi-order (multiple selection possible). The selected options will be listed separately for each individual order within the multi-order. This ensures that the options can easily be connected to the correct customers and orders.</p></td>
