<td class="icon">
<i class="fa icon-tip" title="Tip"></i>
</td>
<td class="content">
<div class="title">Tip: Check orders</div>
<div class="paragraph">
<p>If you want to check whether a customer still has unpaid orders that could be included in a multi-order, then you can search for this customer’s unpaid orders in the <strong>Orders</strong> tab.</p>
</div>
</td>
